Author: Outing App
Title: [ANN] [OUTING] [ICO] The first cryptocurrency dedicated to events and outings
Body: INTRODUCTION  Outing Project is the first community app (iOS & Android) dedicated to events and outings in real time. The app integrates its own cryptocurrency OTG based on ERC20 Protocol, this crypto rewards users for notify events to the community. The crypto can be used anywhere in the world with Outing Card which permit to transfer OTG to the card and change it into any FIAT currency.  Say hello to the "Waze of events" !  FEATURES  iOS & Android App  Outing is a free app that will be released Q4 2018. It will resolve the problem of "what can we do today, tonight ?" thanks to the community which indicate and notify events and outings : street dancers, musician, concert, exhibitions, museum, parties in nightclub....  An unique cryptocurrency : OTG  Outing integrates its own cryptocurrency which rewards users for their daily use, it will be the crypto of events and outings.  A debit Outing card  This card will permit to users to spend their OTG by changing it to any FIAT currency : buy online, take drink with friends....  Our mission is to democratize cryptocurrency to everyone !  SUPPLY AND DISTRIBUTION  Total Supply : 560000000 Decimals : 8 Token Ticker : OTG Token Name : Outing  Outing Reserve (for rewards users) locked 6 months  : 56% Outing ICO : 36% Outing Team (locked 1 year) : 8%  ICO INFORMATIONS  Start : 8th January 2018 at 00.00.00 AM End : 18th February 2018 at 23.59.00 PM  Soft Cap : 20 000 000 OTG Normal Cap : 50 000 000 OTG Optimal Cap : 100 000 000 OTG Hard Cap : 201 600 000 OTG  Price Tier 1 : 0.07$ - 08/01/18 to 21/01/18 Price Tier 2 : 0.08$ - 22/01/18 to 04/02/18 Price Tier 3 : 0.09$ - 05/02/18 to 11/02/18 Price Tier 4 : 0.10$ - 12/02/18 to 18/02/18  LINKS  Official Website : https://www.outing-app.com WhitePaper : https://docs.wixstatic.com/ugd/3880ee_ae7d4618754a4f8a81cf5fc056d66931.pdf Twitter : www.twitter.com/outingappli Facebook : www.facebook.com/outingapp Github : https://github.com/OutingApp/hellocommunity Slack : outingoffice-app.slack.com  ICO WatchList : https://icowatchlist.com/ico/outing
